Hello <%= @user.login %>,

vpsAdmin monitoring has detected an issue affecting your service.

Alert: <%= @event.label %>
State: <%= @event.state %>
<% if @event.respond_to?(:issue) && @event.issue -%>
Issue: <%= @event.issue %>
<% end -%>
<% if @object -%>
Object: <%= @object.class.name %> #<%= @object.respond_to?(:id) ? @object.id : @event.row_id %>
<% else -%>
Object: <%= @event.class_name %> #<%= @event.row_id %>
<% end -%>
<% if @base_url && !@base_url.empty? -%>
vpsAdmin: <%= @base_url %>
<% end -%>

Best regards,

vpsAdmin
